title: Yevgeni Latyshonok
text:
Yevgeni Igorevich Latyshonok (; born 21 June 1998) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Baltika%20Kaliningrad">FC Baltika Kaliningrad</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Professional%20Football%20League">Russian Professional Football League</a> for <a href="FC%20Krasnodar-2">FC Krasnodar-2</a> on 5 April 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Chayka%20Peschanokopskoye">FC Chayka Peschanokopskoye</a>.
On 23 July 2019, he joined <a href="FC%20Baltika%20Kaliningrad">FC Baltika Kaliningrad</a>. He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for Baltika on 10 August 2019 in a game against <a href="FC%20Mordovia%20Saransk">FC Mordovia Saransk</a>.
